Match one part exactly and match a range on another part

trace分析优化器如何选择执行计划
Sending data表示MySQL线程开始访问数据行并把结果返回客户端
explain extended + show warnings 查看优化器改写
mysql> explain select * from film where title = 'WRATH MILE';
| id | select_type | table | partitions | type | possible_keys | key | key_len | ref | rows | filtered |
| 1 | SIMPLE | film | NULL | ref | idx_title | idx_title | 767 | const | 1 | 100.00 | NULL |
非唯一索引或唯一索引前缀扫描
聚簇索引和非聚簇索引
最适合出现索引的列是出现在WHERE子句或连接子句中的列
例如：ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE CASCADE
自动增长列必须是索引
